ns0:svg.ns0:text: Look carefully at the image showing Elements of the weather. Use what you see to answer the questions that follow.
1. What are the main things you see in this picture related to the weather?
2. Can you count and list the different types of clouds shown in the image?
3. What does the image suggest about the different conditions of the weather?
4. How do the elements of the weather shown in the image affect our daily activities?
5. Imagine you are a weather reporter. Describe the weather scene in the image and predict what might happen next.
